Class MSIConfigurationForAppService

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.azure.v3.credentials.MSIConfigurationForAppService
  • public class MSIConfigurationForAppService
extends java.lang.Object
    Defines the configuration to be used for retrieving access token from within an app-service with system assigned MSI enabled.
